 .../browser/pr/krtPullRequestEditorPane.css   | 41 ++++++++++++
 .../browser/pr/krtPullRequestEditorPane.ts    | 65 ++++++++++++++++---
 3 files changed, 128 insertions(+), 11 deletions(-)

